  Relationship among key terms

      Type of Volcano or vent

           * caldera
           * cinder cone
           * hornito
           * lava dome
           * maar
           * mud volcano
           * shield volcano
           * spatter cone
           * stratovolcano

                             Eruption Types

                                  * effusive
                                       + aa
                                       + pahoehoe
                                       + obsidian
                                       + pillow basalt
                                  * debris flows
                                       + lahar
                                       + debris avalanche
                                  * geyser
                                  * hydrovolcanic
                                  * lava fountain
                                  * lava lake
                                  * plinian
                                  * pyroclastic flow
                                  * strombolian
                                  * vulcanian

